model.description: MenuModel instance to define the action items.
model.description_zh: MenuModel 实例来定义措施项。

visible.description: Specifies the visibility of the overlay.

direction.description: Specifies the opening direction of actions.
direction.type: left / right / up / down / up-left / up-right / down-left / down-right

transitionDelay.description: Transition delay step for each action item.
transitionDelay.description_zh: 每个操作项的转换延迟步骤。

type.description: Specifies the opening type of actions.

mask.description: Whether to show a mask element behind the speeddial.
mask.description_zh: 是否在快速拨号后面显示遮罩元素。

hideOnClickOutside.description: Whether the actions close when clicked outside.
hideOnClickOutside.description_zh: 在外部单击操作时是否关闭。

buttonClass.description: Style class of the button element.
buttonClass.description_zh: 按钮元素的 Style 类。

maskStyle.description: Inline style of the mask element.

maskClass.description: Style class of the mask element.
maskClass.description_zh: 掩码元素的 Style 类。

showIcon.description: Show icon of the button element.

hideIcon.description: Hide icon of the button element.

rotateAnimation.description: Defined to rotate showIcon when hideIcon is not present.
rotateAnimation.description_zh: 定义为在 hideIcon 不存在时旋转 showIcon。

tooltipOptions.description: Whether to display the tooltip on items. The modifiers of Tooltip can be used like an object in it. Valid keys are 'event' and 'position'.
tooltipOptions.description_zh: 是否在项目上显示工具提示。Tooltip 的修改器可以像其中的对象一样使用。有效键为 'event' 和 'position'。

aria-label.description: Defines a string value that labels an interactive list element.
aria-label.description_zh: 定义一个字符串值，该值标记交互式列表元素。

aria-labelledby.description: Identifier of the underlying list element.
aria-labelledby.description_zh: 基础列表元素的标识符。

pt.description: Used to pass attributes to DOM elements inside the component.
pt.description_zh: 用于将属性传递给组件内部的 DOM 元素。

ptOptions.description: Used to configure passthrough(pt) options of the component.
ptOptions.description_zh: 用于配置组件的直通 （pt） 选项。

unstyled.description: When enabled, it removes component related styles in the core.
unstyled.description_zh: 启用后，它会删除核心中与组件相关的样式。

events.name: click
events.description: Fired when the button element clicked.

events.name: show
events.description: Fired when the actions are visible.

events.name: hide
events.description: Fired when the actions are hidden.

events.name: focus
events.description: Callback to invoke when the component receives focus.
events.description_zh: 在组件接收焦点时调用的回调。

events.name: blur
events.description: Callback to invoke when the component loses focus.
events.description_zh: 在组件失去焦点时调用的回调。
